title: NASA, 17 May BP oil slick in the Gulf of Mexico, World, 2010
name: NASA, 17 May BP oil slick in the Gulf of Mexico, World, 2010
description: NASA has released a satellite image of the oil slick dated 17 May 2010, the oil slick shows a tail moving in the south south east direction, perhaps close to the Gulf loop current.

author.source: NASA Rapid Response satellite image website
